NAME
	scars - list of possible scars

DESCRIPTION
	A person with all possible scars looks like this:

Graah has a scar on his left leg, his right leg, his nose, his left arm,
his right arm, his left hand, his right hand, his forehead, his left cheek,
his right cheek, his chest, his jaw, his left side, his right side, his
back, his pelvis, his stomach and his neck.

